data.description:
Welcome to this solar-paid home with a split floor plan, located in a highly desirable neighborhood. This residence boasts a chef's dream kitchen, complete with a stovetop featuring 5 burners and a grill, as well as a custom-designed walk-in pantry.
As you step inside, you will be greeted by the elegance of wood shutters throughout the home. This property also offers added security with a large safe that will remain in the primary rooms closet. 
Technology enthusiasts will appreciate the surround sound and intercom system. In addition, you can experience the ultimate relaxation in the inground swimming pool, which features alternate covers to suit your preferences.
For those with recreational vehicles, this home offers the convenience of two electric RV gates and a work shed equipped with electricity, shelves, and A/C .
Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a property that combines functionality, comfort, and style.
